  <summary date="2021-09-07T15:26:35Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Jeanette Acosta Invest in Women's Health Act of 2021

This bill directs the Department of Health and Human Services to establish&#160;a series of programs to increase access to cancer screenings for women.

These programs include demonstration projects to

 train certain health care providers to screen for breast and cervical cancer, and increase co-testing of human papillomavirus (HPV) and cervical cancer among populations that have disproportionate rates of cervical cancer.</summary>
